rComments: So down to earth. Wants you to love the subject instead of worrying about points. Offers tons of extra credit and will sacrifice all his time to help you
Great Professor! Take the class! Would recommend saving it for senior year so you can kick back and relax for the semester!

He's a great professor. The exams are based on the lecture slides.  Lectures are not mandatory but there are iclicker questions.  Discussions are worth 39% of your course grade.  The class is very easy.  There are weekly pre-discussion videos and questions to answer.  There is only  one research project in this course.  Extra credit is offered.

Ben is a great professor. His class isn't hard and the topic is somewhat interesting. The tests are pretty easy if you just review the lecture slides that he posts online.  This class is easy so don't take if you like a huge challenge.

Awesome professor! Prodigiously talented in both intelligence and passion. Kind and accommodating - I had a small conflict with an exam and he allowed me to take it in his office at a later date, no problem. You will learn so much and be captivated no matter your major. He cares for your input and made me consider switching to IB! TAKE THIS CLASS

Be warned, No dinosaurs until after 8 weeks. The first half of the class is insufferable, but the second half is really cool. Ben Clegg can be a bit confusing and can go off on tangents, but he's a sweetheart and SO knowledgable. If you can stick it through the evolution of time, then I would recommend this course. Also, study: I went from C+ to A-

Extremely helpful and nice. I really enjoyed the class. It is a lot of work, so if you have no interest in the subject I wouldn't recommend it. If you enjoy the subject of biology then this class would be perfect for you.

Really easy class! you have to go to class for iClickers, but as long as you go to 70% of classes you get a 100% in attendance. Easy tests as long as you review the material. Usually curved. no textbook, the final is not cumulative.
Amazing teacher! He is so passionate in what he is teaching and you learn a lot from him. Easy tests, and easy class over all! RECOMMEND!

Professor Clegg is really excited about his subject but his teaching style is not very engaging. The class was also a little disorganized and he took over a month to get exam grades back. The discussions were completely pointless and the material was a little difficult for a 100-level class. Would not recommend.
Awesome TA, discussion helped me get through IB 150
Tries hard but is really hard to understand.
